1
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:34,520
=Lady Liberty=

2
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:37,940
=Episode 17=

3
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:42,955
I will be home in half an hour.

4
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:52,040
You are still here?

5
00:01:54,555 --> 00:01:56,040
Gu Yan has not submitted his draft.

6
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:57,240
I want to wait a bit longer.

7
00:01:57,440 --> 00:02:00,040
If he still has not replied at 9 PM

8
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:01,120
or submitted the draft,

9
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,220
I will have to go find him.

10
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:02,980
I will call him.

11
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:04,530
No need. His phone is off.

12
00:02:04,666 --> 00:02:05,850
I have been calling all night.

13
00:02:08,040 --> 00:02:08,840
I will go find him.

14
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:09,990
You go back and rest first.

15
00:02:10,040 --> 00:02:11,990
Once he submits it,
you still need to typeset it.

16
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:13,560
He is not at his place.

17
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,470
I checked this afternoon.

18
00:02:14,480 --> 00:02:15,000
I see.

19
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,240
After you get home, tell Zhou Mei

20
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:18,177
I will be back later
and ask her to wait for me.

21
00:02:26,500 --> 00:02:29,420
(Keeping stories alive together.)

22
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:08,680
Is Gu Yan here, San Mei?

23
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:09,240
No.

24
00:03:10,044 --> 00:03:11,120
Do you know where he went?

25
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:12,520
I cannot reach him.

26
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:14,488
His phone is off, and he is not at home.

27
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:16,760
Other than your company,

28
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:20,240
his place, and here, I don't know
where else he would go.

29
00:03:20,577 --> 00:03:21,880
He does not have other friends.

30
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,720
If he contacts you,

31
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,640
please tell him to call me back.

32
00:03:25,650 --> 00:03:27,680
Also, ask him to send
the draft as soon as possible.

33
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:28,080
Thank you.

34
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,600
So what you are worried
about is where he is,

35
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:31,990
or whether he can submit the draft?

36
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:32,800
To me,

37
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:34,000
both matter.

38
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:35,240
It is the same issue.

39
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:36,840
He treats you like family.

40
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,600
You treat him as a tool to make money.

41
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:45,560
You should understand that relationships

42
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,440
are not either-or.

43
00:04:24,220 --> 00:04:25,210
You didn't find Gu Yan?

44
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:27,420
No draft either?

45
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:28,560
No.

46
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:32,960
Looks like today is not a good day.

47
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,620
Tell me about you first.

48
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,030
Three against one.

49
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:39,880
What happened?

50
00:04:43,977 --> 00:04:45,400
I think Zhang Yousen already knows

51
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:46,520
about Lawyer Bei and me.

52
00:04:47,311 --> 00:04:48,160
So he deliberately

53
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,720
brought Lawyer Bei and his wife.

54
00:04:50,288 --> 00:04:51,533
He was the one against three.

55
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:54,280
What do you mean by you and Lawyer Bei?

56
00:04:55,088 --> 00:04:56,622
What is going on between you two?

57
00:04:58,577 --> 00:04:59,533
She does not know?

58
00:05:04,180 --> 00:05:04,740
That is right.

59
00:05:05,555 --> 00:05:06,840
Exactly what you are thinking.

60
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,840
Welcome to the adult world.

61
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:12,200
Then, you...

62
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:13,760
What about you and Zhang Yousen?

63
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:16,120
They are boss and employee.

64
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,240
Just listen.

65
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:18,640
Do not ask so much.

66
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:22,760
So, how did Lawyer Bei perform today?

67
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:26,310
Perfect boss.

68
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:27,840
Perfect husband.

69
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:28,955
Zero as a lover.

70
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,680
He probably didn't know

71
00:05:31,866 --> 00:05:33,260
Zhang Yousen had invited his wife.

72
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,760
But the moment he saw her,

73
00:05:37,320 --> 00:05:39,180
he had already decided to give me up.

74
00:05:40,300 --> 00:05:41,120
Makes sense.

75
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:43,920
What else could he do?

76
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:47,320
If it is really like you said,

77
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:48,800
that his wife

78
00:05:48,830 --> 00:05:49,600
and his subordinate

79
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:50,840
have cornered him,

80
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,280
what else could he do

81
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:53,266
other than give you up?

82
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:56,800
Consort Yang was favored above all,

83
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:58,000
yet in the end,

84
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,760
she was forced to die at Mawei Slope.

85
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:01,600
Who do you think you are?

86
00:06:08,111 --> 00:06:09,444
Harsh words are hard to hear.

87
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:11,680
Take it or leave it.

88
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,600
But in this situation,

89
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:16,955
you should be paying
attention to Zhang Yousen.

90
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,600
If he arranged

91
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:20,960
all of this,

92
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,840
then the one feeling uneasy now

93
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:24,480
should be Lawyer Bei.

94
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:28,320
Zhang Yousen is about to go to Chengdu.

95
00:06:28,888 --> 00:06:29,977
No matter how complicated,

96
00:06:30,244 --> 00:06:31,120
this will be settled.

97
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:32,800
How can you be sure

98
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:33,960
he will still go?

99
00:06:36,444 --> 00:06:38,466
Miss this chance,
and there will not be another.

100
00:06:39,400 --> 00:06:40,480
If he does not go,

101
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,440
he will remain under Lawyer Bei

102
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,160
for years.

103
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:46,320
If he were as calculating as you say,

104
00:06:46,711 --> 00:06:48,640
he would not give up
a fast promotion opportunity

105
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,520
just to stay for me.

106
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,520
Originally,

107
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:54,040
he wanted both love and a career.

108
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,760
Now, he can only choose one.

109
00:06:56,577 --> 00:06:57,622
He will choose a career.

110
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:58,880
That is certain.

111
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,240
If he stays,

112
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:02,200
he may lose both.

113
00:07:05,177 --> 00:07:07,244
I would rather believe
the Zhang Yousen I know

114
00:07:07,266 --> 00:07:08,640
is just someone ruled by love.

115
00:07:10,755 --> 00:07:12,440
Those who should
be ruled by love are not.

116
00:07:12,622 --> 00:07:15,022
Those who should not be ruled by love
only become more determined.

117
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,640
Who is ruled by love?

118
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:18,320
My dad.

119
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,040
Starting today,

120
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,560
he is going to the gym.

121
00:07:22,740 --> 00:07:23,760
He said that in a few days,

122
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:25,240
he will come to show us the results.

123
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:28,600
He told me he has found someone

124
00:07:28,933 --> 00:07:30,680
to spend the rest of his life with.

125
00:07:46,577 --> 00:07:47,880
It's Lin Zhanqiao, right?

126
00:07:49,133 --> 00:07:52,000
A few days ago, he already asked me
to pass the message to you.

127
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,040
I really

128
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,640
held it in until now.

129
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:55,520
If I didn't say it...

130
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:56,560
Stop laughing.

131
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,200
I was afraid

132
00:07:57,200 --> 00:07:59,040
he would come himself
and tell you directly.

133
00:07:59,111 --> 00:08:00,380
And you will be startled, right?

134
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,240
You have already shocked me.

135
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:05,000
Ms. Lin, my dad's relationships

136
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,000
have nothing to do with me.

137
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,280
We're different.

138
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:08,640
Just treat us separately.

139
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:10,755
Tell your dad to stop.
There is no chance.

140
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:12,600
He is not Lin Zhanqiao's type.

141
00:08:29,660 --> 00:08:31,940
(5 messages from Gu Yan: [image])

142
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:03,000
Where are you?

143
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,800
Why are you not answering my calls?

144
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:05,800
Not in a good mood.

145
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:07,422
Out getting some air.

146
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,280
Do not worry.

147
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,280
I didn't go far.

148
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,240
From Shanghai,

149
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,977
it is at most an hour and a half drive.

150
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,800
Will you come back today?

151
00:09:17,155 --> 00:09:18,400
If you are coming back,

152
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:19,560
I can come find you later.

153
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,680
Not sure.

154
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:24,720
If I don't come back,

155
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:26,680
will you come find me?

156
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:28,720
After work,

157
00:09:29,177 --> 00:09:31,066
no matter how late, I can wait.

158
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:33,240
I just want to talk to you.

159
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:35,800
I know what you
want to talk to me about.

160
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,680
Right now, I am working with He Han.

161
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:40,320
We are putting on a show for Mr. Fan.

162
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:42,320
We need him to believe

163
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:44,800
Chenxing's future includes He Han.

164
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:45,920
So he will invest in us.

165
00:09:47,644 --> 00:09:49,711
The contract will be
signed in the next few days.

166
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:52,480
So, I hope you can keep
this confidential for now.

167
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,680
Even if I believe what you said,

168
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:56,320
even if I accept

169
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:58,080
He Han's influence on you,

170
00:09:58,880 --> 00:09:59,680
aside from that,

171
00:10:01,280 --> 00:10:02,600
can I have an answer?

172
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:05,960
Do you love me?

173
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:16,720
If I continue to give you

174
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,920
all my time and energy,

175
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,760
can that make you love me?

176
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:30,360
Whether I love you or not

177
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:32,440
has nothing to do with what you do

178
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:33,960
or what you will do.

179
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,640
I think you do love me.

180
00:10:36,088 --> 00:10:37,480
That's why I just keep writing

181
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,760
every single day

182
00:10:38,760 --> 00:10:40,200
without stopping.

183
00:10:40,880 --> 00:10:42,000
I am not doing it

184
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,200
for the money you mentioned.

185
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:46,360
I am poor.

186
00:10:48,280 --> 00:10:49,320
I need money.

187
00:10:49,880 --> 00:10:52,920
But I have never thought
about how much I want to earn.

188
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,480
Everything I do is for you.

189
00:10:58,640 --> 00:11:00,080
I write well for you.

190
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:03,120
I reach the top rankings for you.

191
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:05,040
Even when I earn a lot of money,
it is for you.

192
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:11,120
I just hope you can...

193
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:15,280
You can...

194
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:18,040
You can like me,

195
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:19,520
love me,

196
00:11:20,920 --> 00:11:22,400
and not leave me.

197
00:11:24,800 --> 00:11:26,720
I hope everything you do

198
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:28,120
is for yourself.

199
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:30,333
I care about you, and I look after you

200
00:11:30,520 --> 00:11:31,680
because I am your boss

201
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:32,640
and you are my employee.

202
00:11:33,511 --> 00:11:35,520
But I hope you can be
clear about your position

203
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:36,880
and the relationship between us.

204
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:39,900
We can talk about money,

205
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,240
cooperation,

206
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:43,480
and compensation.

207
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:44,444
All of that is fine.

208
00:11:45,155 --> 00:11:46,666
But we don't talk about feelings.

209
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,040
You never said this to me before.

210
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,520
Then, take it as me saying it now.

211
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,466
I don't want to write anymore.

212
00:12:10,511 --> 00:12:13,040
I don't know why I have to write these
meaningless things every day.

213
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:14,133
Find someone else to write.

214
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:34,320
I want to see you now.

215
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:41,120
Morning.

216
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:42,520
Morning, Ms. Lin.

217
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:44,840
Has Gu Yan contacted you?

218
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:46,560
He must submit tonight.

219
00:12:46,880 --> 00:12:49,080
Otherwise, we will miss the update
tomorrow afternoon.

220
00:12:49,880 --> 00:12:50,720
And now, Dingqi

221
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:52,040
is about to sign with us, right?

222
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,960
If our most important author

223
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:54,720
does not submit,

224
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:56,000
it will affect us.

225
00:12:58,333 --> 00:12:59,760
He is probably not in Shanghai.

226
00:13:00,133 --> 00:13:02,200
He sent me a few photos.
I will send them to you.

227
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:03,360
Check where that is.

228
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:04,070
Okay.

229
00:13:05,288 --> 00:13:07,000
Zhang Yousen said he is not leaving.

230
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:51,555
Some things are not
convenient to say at the office.

231
00:13:52,022 --> 00:13:53,222
I want to stay in Shanghai.

232
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:58,240
So, you chose love over a career?

233
00:13:58,520 --> 00:13:59,120
I want both.

234
00:13:59,280 --> 00:13:59,920
On what basis?

235
00:14:00,333 --> 00:14:01,688
Your relationship with Zhou Mei.

236
00:14:02,711 --> 00:14:04,720
That day, when she asked me
to act as her boyfriend

237
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:05,670
to have dinner with you,

238
00:14:05,680 --> 00:14:06,520
I already noticed.

239
00:14:09,377 --> 00:14:11,480
That day, when you proposed
and asked me to join,

240
00:14:11,880 --> 00:14:13,000
I figured it out as well.

241
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,920
Then, my wife suddenly appeared.

242
00:14:16,680 --> 00:14:18,160
That was your doing too, right?

243
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:21,760
Originally,

244
00:14:22,422 --> 00:14:23,733
if she had accepted the ring

245
00:14:23,822 --> 00:14:25,380
and our relationship had been confirmed,

246
00:14:25,390 --> 00:14:26,720
everything would have worked out.

247
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:28,320
What do you want now?

248
00:14:28,688 --> 00:14:31,360
Are you trying to use my relationship
with Zhou Mei to threaten me?

249
00:14:31,800 --> 00:14:32,760
You have no evidence.

250
00:14:32,760 --> 00:14:34,000
I could turn around and sue you.

251
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,244
I care too much about Zhou Mei

252
00:14:35,520 --> 00:14:36,840
to use her as a tool.

253
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:40,640
In Wangyue Legal Consulting,

254
00:14:40,955 --> 00:14:42,720
Zhou Mei is
the legal representative, right?

255
00:14:42,780 --> 00:14:44,860
(Business License.
Legal Representative. Zhou Mei)

256
00:14:48,920 --> 00:14:50,120
All outsourced projects

257
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:53,200
cannot be registered
under my or my family's name.

258
00:14:53,920 --> 00:14:56,080
Zhou Mei is just a name on paper.

259
00:14:56,080 --> 00:14:57,200
So, Zhou Mei knows

260
00:14:57,210 --> 00:14:58,670
that Wangyue is under investigation?

261
00:14:58,680 --> 00:14:59,355
She knows.

262
00:15:00,560 --> 00:15:01,320
I already told her.

263
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:03,440
This matter will be handled by someone.

264
00:15:03,520 --> 00:15:04,600
So she should also know

265
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,960
about the two sets of
accounts in the company,

266
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:07,760
right?

267
00:15:14,400 --> 00:15:15,160
What do you mean?

268
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:17,920
Some of Wangyue's projects

269
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:19,160
passed through my hands.

270
00:15:23,280 --> 00:15:24,080
(From what I know,)

271
00:15:24,222 --> 00:15:25,680
(there are issues with the amounts.)

272
00:15:25,820 --> 00:15:27,266
(Third quarter financial statement)
(So I suspect)

273
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:29,920
(other projects would not hold up either.)

274
00:15:32,520 --> 00:15:33,760
You have a good memory.

275
00:15:33,888 --> 00:15:35,755
A good memory is not as
reliable as written records.

276
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,200
I keep a record

277
00:15:37,311 --> 00:15:39,000
of every document I have handled.

278
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:41,800
Fine.

279
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:44,280
Then,

280
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:46,360
you can check them.

281
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:49,680
If there are any issues,
we can correct them together.

282
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:50,760
I think you should

283
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:52,120
let Zhou Mei know everything.

284
00:15:52,622 --> 00:15:54,760
I am telling you, this has
nothing to do with Zhou Mei.

285
00:15:54,760 --> 00:15:55,680
But once it happens,

286
00:15:55,680 --> 00:15:57,866
as the legal representative,
it directly involves her.

287
00:15:58,160 --> 00:15:58,680
I know.

288
00:15:59,640 --> 00:16:00,520
I will handle it.

289
00:16:04,920 --> 00:16:06,400
You decided not to leave

290
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:08,240
because you are worried about Zhou Mei?

291
00:16:08,377 --> 00:16:09,600
Lawyer Bei, I have a proposal.

292
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:10,600
See if it works.

293
00:16:12,120 --> 00:16:13,800
The Wangyue matter is a bit tricky now.

294
00:16:14,160 --> 00:16:15,200
As a senior lawyer,

295
00:16:15,280 --> 00:16:17,044
it's not convenient for
you to intervene directly.

296
00:16:17,333 --> 00:16:18,177
How about this?

297
00:16:18,400 --> 00:16:19,288
I handle it for you.

298
00:16:19,577 --> 00:16:20,866
But you have to promise me

299
00:16:20,955 --> 00:16:22,400
that none of the figures you give me

300
00:16:22,520 --> 00:16:23,440
are concealed.

301
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:24,680
And...

302
00:16:25,720 --> 00:16:26,920
my condition is that I become

303
00:16:26,920 --> 00:16:28,360
the youngest partner in the firm.

304
00:16:28,560 --> 00:16:29,200
And soon.

305
00:16:29,288 --> 00:16:30,160
That is impossible.

306
00:16:31,200 --> 00:16:32,040
Your experience

307
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:33,640
is not convincing enough.

308
00:16:34,555 --> 00:16:35,520
You are the boss.

309
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:36,640
You must have a way.

310
00:16:37,755 --> 00:16:38,730
What about Zhou Mei?

311
00:16:38,880 --> 00:16:40,288
You don't want to involve her.

312
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:42,400
I step in as the one who saves her.

313
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:44,760
The important thing is,

314
00:16:45,520 --> 00:16:47,320
I will keep this
confidential from Mrs. Bei.

315
00:16:52,160 --> 00:16:52,560
Fine.

316
00:16:54,640 --> 00:16:56,920
Show me what you are capable of

317
00:16:57,920 --> 00:17:00,080
and let me see
how cleanly you handle it.

318
00:17:11,511 --> 00:17:12,520
Ms. Lin, I am coming in.

319
00:17:14,520 --> 00:17:15,000
What is it?

320
00:17:15,320 --> 00:17:15,880
I found it.

321
00:17:16,240 --> 00:17:16,800
Found what?

322
00:17:16,880 --> 00:17:17,520
Where Gu Yan is.

323
00:17:18,377 --> 00:17:19,240
How did you find it?

324
00:17:19,600 --> 00:17:20,120
My dad.

325
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:21,880
I sent him the photo of the scenery.

326
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:23,480
He builds properties everywhere,

327
00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:24,720
so he has been to that place.

328
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:27,520
Why would he go to Luxu Ancient Town?

329
00:17:28,240 --> 00:17:29,800
Ms. Lin, do you want to go check now?

330
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:31,320
Listen.

331
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:32,800
Find an excuse

332
00:17:32,880 --> 00:17:34,200
and call Zhao Lanxin's company.

333
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:35,155
See if she is there.

334
00:17:35,860 --> 00:17:37,533
What does Zhao Lanxin
have to do with it?

335
00:17:37,555 --> 00:17:39,244
That address is Zhao Lanxin's hometown.

336
00:17:39,800 --> 00:17:40,840
For Gu Yan to go there,

337
00:17:40,840 --> 00:17:42,560
someone must have
arranged it in advance.

338
00:17:42,888 --> 00:17:44,800
With his personality, he would rather
stay in an internet cafe all day

339
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:46,720
than go into the mountains
to stay at a guesthouse.

340
00:17:46,800 --> 00:17:47,840
Alright, I will do it now.

341
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:15,440
Zhangzhu,

342
00:18:16,460 --> 00:18:17,840
print out Gu Yan's last ten chapters,

343
00:18:17,840 --> 00:18:20,080
and the outline for
the next twenty chapters, right away.

344
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:22,040
So he really is not submitting?

345
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:24,240
We prepare for the worst.

346
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:26,520
We cannot rely on others.

347
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:27,640
Depending on others is risky.

348
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:29,240
The moment something goes wrong,

349
00:18:29,360 --> 00:18:30,360
we will fall hard.

350
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:33,160
Understood.

351
00:18:44,480 --> 00:18:45,822
You don't plan to keep writing?

352
00:18:49,760 --> 00:18:50,800
If I stop,

353
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:53,440
I will stop writing for any company.

354
00:18:54,520 --> 00:18:55,160
In the end,

355
00:18:56,320 --> 00:18:57,320
this is

356
00:18:58,360 --> 00:18:59,520
a solitary battle.

357
00:18:59,920 --> 00:19:00,680
Except for myself,

358
00:19:01,680 --> 00:19:02,960
who cannot walk away at will,

359
00:19:02,960 --> 00:19:04,240
everyone else can

360
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:06,320
come and go as they please.

361
00:19:08,280 --> 00:19:08,920
I have tried it.

362
00:19:09,960 --> 00:19:11,200
I don't like this kind of work.

363
00:19:12,555 --> 00:19:13,680
What do you want to do?

364
00:19:14,177 --> 00:19:16,177
Go back to the internet cafe
as a manager?

365
00:19:18,044 --> 00:19:19,600
It is not the same as playing games.

366
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:21,160
We have a team.

367
00:19:21,960 --> 00:19:24,000
Our team moves together.

368
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:29,160
You were in the internet cafe,
playing games while writing,

369
00:19:29,160 --> 00:19:30,688
and Lin Zhanqiao discovered you.

370
00:19:31,240 --> 00:19:32,040
If it were me,

371
00:19:32,480 --> 00:19:33,600
I would let you stay there,

372
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:35,720
keep playing and writing.

373
00:19:39,311 --> 00:19:41,066
You started writing online fiction

374
00:19:41,133 --> 00:19:42,400
because of Phantom Knight, right?

375
00:19:44,200 --> 00:19:45,920
He Han and Hong Qigong

376
00:19:46,080 --> 00:19:46,960
are nothing.

377
00:19:47,520 --> 00:19:48,680
Only Phantom Knight

378
00:19:48,680 --> 00:19:50,440
is an untouchable legend.

379
00:19:52,022 --> 00:19:53,644
It is a pity he stopped writing.

380
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:55,800
The genre he was best at

381
00:19:55,840 --> 00:19:56,800
was game transmigration.

382
00:19:57,480 --> 00:19:58,480
If you write that genre,

383
00:19:58,480 --> 00:19:59,888
you will not be worse than him.

384
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:01,760
What you are writing now,
Drunk Old Friend,

385
00:20:02,240 --> 00:20:03,600
is an outline created

386
00:20:03,600 --> 00:20:04,800
by He Han and Lin Zhanqiao.

387
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:06,240
It is not yours.

388
00:20:07,280 --> 00:20:08,240
So, you feel constrained,

389
00:20:08,422 --> 00:20:09,800
like you are being controlled.

390
00:20:11,377 --> 00:20:12,577
Go back to the internet cafe.

391
00:20:13,040 --> 00:20:14,560
Go back to your familiar friends.

392
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:15,960
Write stories you know.

393
00:20:16,360 --> 00:20:17,800
Become the next Phantom Knight.

394
00:20:18,800 --> 00:20:20,200
I will not invest in your novel.

395
00:20:21,330 --> 00:20:22,740
I will invest in your internet cafe.

396
00:20:33,155 --> 00:20:34,555
Let me think about it.

397
00:20:38,560 --> 00:20:39,400
From what we can see,

398
00:20:39,720 --> 00:20:41,200
the updated content has diverged

399
00:20:41,200 --> 00:20:42,260
from the original outline.

400
00:20:42,400 --> 00:20:43,622
That was due to the new map.

401
00:20:43,666 --> 00:20:45,640
Gu Yan had already
adjusted the earlier chapters.

402
00:20:45,640 --> 00:20:47,280
Originally, after this chapter,

403
00:20:47,280 --> 00:20:48,600
he planned to revise the outline.

404
00:20:48,720 --> 00:20:49,640
We revise it for him.

405
00:20:49,760 --> 00:20:50,520
There is no time.

406
00:20:50,520 --> 00:20:51,560
It is already 2:30 PM.

407
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:53,240
If the submission is due

408
00:20:53,240 --> 00:20:53,880
at 6 PM,

409
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:56,711
revising the outline and having someone
continue writing will not be enough.

410
00:20:56,755 --> 00:20:58,377
We don't need to revise everything.

411
00:20:58,480 --> 00:21:00,200
We organize the updated direction first,

412
00:21:00,280 --> 00:21:01,200
and then start writing.

413
00:21:01,240 --> 00:21:03,240
Who can write in his place?

414
00:21:09,680 --> 00:21:10,160
I will try.

415
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:11,000
Ms. Lin,

416
00:21:11,355 --> 00:21:12,760
Dingqi Platform's legal team is here.

417
00:21:15,080 --> 00:21:15,920
So early.

418
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:19,920
I have an idea, Ms. Lin.

419
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:22,000
When Gu Yan

420
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:23,200
wrote this part,

421
00:21:23,320 --> 00:21:24,440
you went to see Mr. He Han

422
00:21:24,440 --> 00:21:26,333
and adjusted the content
together at his hotel.

423
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:27,320
If Gu Yan

424
00:21:27,320 --> 00:21:29,000
followed his approach,

425
00:21:29,010 --> 00:21:30,444
Mr. He Han should have an idea

426
00:21:30,488 --> 00:21:31,733
about how the story develops next.

427
00:21:31,777 --> 00:21:33,066
Do you want me to ask him?

428
00:21:34,040 --> 00:21:34,480
No.

429
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:35,800
We solve our own problems.

430
00:21:37,940 --> 00:21:39,260
(Draft Investment Cooperation Agreement
Chenxing Culture Media Co., Ltd.)

431
00:21:39,280 --> 00:21:40,490
Mr. Fan specifically instructed

432
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:42,640
that all issues be resolved today.

433
00:21:42,911 --> 00:21:44,480
We will pick an auspicious day to sign

434
00:21:44,640 --> 00:21:45,440
and make it public

435
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:46,680
about our strong alliance.

436
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:47,840
Alright.

437
00:21:48,360 --> 00:21:49,160
Let us begin.

438
00:21:49,955 --> 00:21:51,040
We have internally reviewed

439
00:21:51,040 --> 00:21:53,000
the contract content.

440
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:55,240
Our concerns and revisions are...

441
00:21:55,240 --> 00:21:57,100
(Mr. Fan)

442
00:21:59,080 --> 00:21:59,600
Sorry.

443
00:22:07,120 --> 00:22:07,800
Hello, Mr. Fan.

444
00:22:08,360 --> 00:22:09,800
What is going on with Gu Yan?

445
00:22:10,688 --> 00:22:11,840
He is throwing a tantrum?

446
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:13,080
We have barely started,

447
00:22:13,080 --> 00:22:14,200
and he is already acting up?

448
00:22:14,733 --> 00:22:16,960
Our editor called him,
and he would not even pick up.

449
00:22:17,040 --> 00:22:17,900
What does that mean?

450
00:22:19,120 --> 00:22:20,440
Is he planning to leave you

451
00:22:20,440 --> 00:22:21,320
for another company?

452
00:22:22,480 --> 00:22:23,120
Let me tell you,

453
00:22:23,760 --> 00:22:26,040
he is not just offending Chenxing now,

454
00:22:26,360 --> 00:22:27,920
but he is also offending Dingqi.

455
00:22:28,720 --> 00:22:30,160
Offending such a major platform,

456
00:22:30,300 --> 00:22:32,080
he can forget about
staying in this industry.

457
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:33,560
Sorry, Mr. Fan.

458
00:22:33,960 --> 00:22:35,360
We are handling this issue.

459
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:36,800
On one hand,

460
00:22:36,888 --> 00:22:38,560
we are stabilizing
his mood and progress.

461
00:22:38,600 --> 00:22:39,466
On the other hand,

462
00:22:39,680 --> 00:22:40,680
we are also developing

463
00:22:40,680 --> 00:22:42,120
new authors in the same genre.

464
00:22:42,120 --> 00:22:43,320
What if that does not work?

465
00:22:46,480 --> 00:22:48,080
My investment in Chenxing

466
00:22:48,680 --> 00:22:50,200
has not even been announced yet.

467
00:22:51,120 --> 00:22:53,520
And your top author
is already slacking off.

468
00:22:54,320 --> 00:22:55,140
If this gets out,

469
00:22:55,640 --> 00:22:57,480
will people not laugh at me?

470
00:22:59,911 --> 00:23:01,177
So he will not write?

471
00:23:01,440 --> 00:23:02,720
If he refuses, then forget it.

472
00:23:03,960 --> 00:23:04,560
Here is

473
00:23:05,600 --> 00:23:06,790
what I think.

474
00:23:07,720 --> 00:23:08,920
Drunk Old Friend

475
00:23:09,800 --> 00:23:10,960
was originally

476
00:23:12,240 --> 00:23:14,480
based on a story outline
developed by He Han and you,

477
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:14,880
right?

478
00:23:15,400 --> 00:23:17,480
It should have been written by He Han.

479
00:23:19,360 --> 00:23:20,680
Given the situation,

480
00:23:22,040 --> 00:23:23,720
if He Han returns,

481
00:23:24,480 --> 00:23:26,360
it can even become a good story.

482
00:23:26,600 --> 00:23:27,000
Right?

483
00:23:28,960 --> 00:23:29,440
Impossible.

484
00:23:34,840 --> 00:23:35,720
Then, by 9 PM tonight,

485
00:23:36,088 --> 00:23:37,266
the draft must be submitted.

486
00:23:38,280 --> 00:23:39,280
Figure it out yourself.

487
00:23:50,822 --> 00:23:52,733
Does this mean
we are ending the meeting?

488
00:23:53,280 --> 00:23:55,080
Mr. Fan asked us to give you some time

489
00:23:55,320 --> 00:23:57,080
to handle the urgent situation.

490
00:23:57,090 --> 00:23:58,720
We will confirm
the contract another day.

491
00:23:58,760 --> 00:23:59,560
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

492
00:23:59,960 --> 00:24:00,360
Let's go.

493
00:24:03,440 --> 00:24:04,440
What do they mean?

494
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:05,320
They are not signing?

495
00:24:05,440 --> 00:24:06,080
It is deliberate.

496
00:24:06,360 --> 00:24:07,440
If we mishandle this,

497
00:24:07,760 --> 00:24:08,680
they can find fault

498
00:24:08,680 --> 00:24:09,720
and push down our price.

499
00:24:10,400 --> 00:24:11,800
Gu Yan's update cannot go wrong.

500
00:24:11,920 --> 00:24:13,400
Neither timing nor quality can fail.

501
00:24:17,720 --> 00:24:18,720
This outline was created

502
00:24:18,720 --> 00:24:19,720
by you and Gu Yan?

503
00:24:22,880 --> 00:24:23,920
What is this writing?

504
00:24:23,960 --> 00:24:24,920
It is completely off.

505
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:26,960
I built the story framework properly,

506
00:24:26,960 --> 00:24:28,040
and he wrote it like this.

507
00:24:28,040 --> 00:24:29,400
The characters and tone are all off.

508
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:30,780
Then, maybe...

509
00:24:31,200 --> 00:24:32,120
Let it go, then.

510
00:24:32,120 --> 00:24:33,080
I will head back first.

511
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:34,280
My boss already told me

512
00:24:34,280 --> 00:24:35,520
not to come find you.

513
00:24:35,760 --> 00:24:37,040
I came to you myself.

514
00:24:37,800 --> 00:24:38,960
What is she going to do, then?

515
00:24:39,111 --> 00:24:40,288
Write it herself?

516
00:24:40,680 --> 00:24:41,640
If it comes to it,

517
00:24:41,640 --> 00:24:42,980
she will have to write it herself.

518
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:46,511
She brought this on herself.

519
00:24:47,200 --> 00:24:48,160
She should never

520
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:50,000
have used Gu Yan.

521
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:50,760
He is unreliable.

522
00:24:50,760 --> 00:24:51,640
Mr. He Han,

523
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:53,480
can you help my boss?

524
00:24:53,480 --> 00:24:55,240
She is really overwhelmed right now.

525
00:24:58,080 --> 00:24:58,480
Hello.

526
00:24:59,466 --> 00:25:00,480
Are you at the hotel?

527
00:25:00,840 --> 00:25:02,240
When will today's update be ready?

528
00:25:02,444 --> 00:25:03,200
I am writing it now.

529
00:25:03,220 --> 00:25:04,111
I will send it tonight.

530
00:25:05,600 --> 00:25:06,830
Do not say I am not loyal.

531
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:08,466
Everyone has their own burden to carry.

532
00:25:09,977 --> 00:25:11,520
(Request payment)
What is this transfer?

533
00:25:11,640 --> 00:25:12,840
Just some moral support.

534
00:25:13,280 --> 00:25:15,440
Go back and buy everyone
some milk tea or late-night snacks.

535
00:25:15,440 --> 00:25:17,520
Say that Mr. He Han
appreciates everyone's hard work.

536
00:25:18,200 --> 00:25:18,990
Get through tonight,

537
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:20,240
and tomorrow will be a new day.

538
00:25:20,560 --> 00:25:21,480
Come on.

539
00:25:21,780 --> 00:25:22,640
Mr. He Han,

540
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:24,680
you cannot refuse to help my boss.

541
00:25:24,680 --> 00:25:26,640
- I can help, but not with this.
- She is about to lose it.

542
00:25:26,640 --> 00:25:28,000
She is really about to lose it now.

543
00:25:28,320 --> 00:25:29,760
No, how am I supposed to help?

544
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:31,940
I don't even have time
to finish my own update.

545
00:25:32,160 --> 00:25:33,880
And your boss would
never accept my help.

546
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:35,360
She would never come to me for it.

547
00:25:35,800 --> 00:25:36,760
Even if I help her,

548
00:25:36,840 --> 00:25:38,120
you will still get fired

549
00:25:38,120 --> 00:25:39,400
for asking me again and again.

550
00:25:39,720 --> 00:25:40,880
Why did you call me here?

551
00:25:40,880 --> 00:25:42,390
I just wanted to
understand the situation.

552
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:43,920
Now that you understand it,
you still will not help?

553
00:25:43,920 --> 00:25:45,190
- She will be really upset.
- Alright.

554
00:25:45,190 --> 00:25:46,120
Thanks for coming.

555
00:25:46,280 --> 00:25:47,020
Head back now.

556
00:25:47,480 --> 00:25:47,840
Go on.

557
00:25:47,960 --> 00:25:48,560
Bye.

558
00:25:48,640 --> 00:25:48,960
You...

559
00:25:49,480 --> 00:25:50,700
Remember to buy milk tea.

560
00:25:54,400 --> 00:25:55,920
If you don't care about her, I do.

561
00:26:51,480 --> 00:26:52,680
Make some space here.

562
00:26:52,680 --> 00:26:54,590
There is a gap here.
I will check with the backend.

563
00:26:54,600 --> 00:26:55,580
Okay, I will fix it now.

564
00:26:57,120 --> 00:26:57,920
Hey, take a look.

565
00:26:58,120 --> 00:26:58,800
Is this okay?

566
00:27:00,040 --> 00:27:00,680
Move it up.

567
00:27:01,010 --> 00:27:01,660
Okay.

568
00:27:10,000 --> 00:27:10,840
Any news from Gu Yan?

569
00:27:11,120 --> 00:27:12,320
No, he is not answering.

570
00:27:13,480 --> 00:27:14,320
It is almost time.

571
00:27:23,900 --> 00:27:27,140
(Finally...)

572
00:27:55,940 --> 00:27:58,620
(Zhao Lanxin)

573
00:27:58,640 --> 00:28:00,240
Lin Zhanqiao is
going to write it for you.

574
00:28:45,900 --> 00:28:51,340
(End of Chapter)

575
00:29:14,920 --> 00:29:15,240
Hello.

576
00:29:16,240 --> 00:29:16,760
How is it?

577
00:29:16,888 --> 00:29:18,911
It has been a while
since you wrote yourself, right?

578
00:29:19,200 --> 00:29:20,680
Feels a bit off, right?

579
00:29:20,840 --> 00:29:22,840
Especially under this kind of pressure,

580
00:29:22,840 --> 00:29:23,480
it wasn't easy.

581
00:29:23,490 --> 00:29:25,110
When you are done,
I will come find you for a drink.

582
00:29:25,120 --> 00:29:25,900
I have not finished.

583
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:26,933
Do not come find me.

584
00:29:27,960 --> 00:29:29,040
Let me tell you,

585
00:29:29,311 --> 00:29:30,400
don't write narrative.

586
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:32,240
Narrative gives you away too easily.

587
00:29:32,320 --> 00:29:34,320
Sharp readers will notice in a few lines

588
00:29:34,330 --> 00:29:35,640
that it's not the original writer.

589
00:29:35,800 --> 00:29:36,560
Just write dialogue.

590
00:29:37,040 --> 00:29:38,640
The denser, the better.

591
00:29:38,800 --> 00:29:39,840
Stretch it however you can.

592
00:29:40,360 --> 00:29:41,830
Alright, that is it. No time.

593
00:29:51,440 --> 00:29:52,120
Guys,

594
00:29:52,300 --> 00:29:54,060
Mr. He Han is treating
everyone to milk tea.

595
00:29:54,060 --> 00:29:55,200
Come on.

596
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:56,350
There are desserts, too.

597
00:29:56,350 --> 00:29:57,520
- From Mr. He Han.
- Here.

598
00:29:57,520 --> 00:29:58,960
It has to be Mr. He Han.

599
00:29:58,960 --> 00:29:59,570
Come. Here.

600
00:29:59,680 --> 00:30:01,690
- Still thinking of Chenxing this late.
- Here.

601
00:30:01,710 --> 00:30:03,890
- Unlike Gu Yan.
- Dessert, too.

602
00:30:03,950 --> 00:30:05,790
- Wins an award and drops everything.
- Dessert.

603
00:30:05,830 --> 00:30:06,800
You know,

604
00:30:06,920 --> 00:30:09,210
I have seen plenty of
delays and missed updates.

605
00:30:09,280 --> 00:30:10,920
- But someone this bold?
- Thanks.

606
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:12,340
This is a first.

607
00:30:12,400 --> 00:30:14,040
Just got popular for a few days,

608
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:15,680
and he already went missing,

609
00:30:15,830 --> 00:30:17,880
- leaving such a mess for Ms. Lin.
- Do you want it?

610
00:30:17,930 --> 00:30:19,780
Who is going to fill in?

611
00:30:20,480 --> 00:30:21,680
Can you keep your voice down?

612
00:30:21,680 --> 00:30:22,920
Afraid she cannot hear you?

613
00:30:23,200 --> 00:30:25,440
The one suffering the most is Ms. Lin.

614
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:27,000
She spent so much time

615
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:27,920
and effort

616
00:30:28,040 --> 00:30:28,760
training him.

617
00:30:29,120 --> 00:30:31,120
And right before
Dingqi Platform's investment,

618
00:30:31,130 --> 00:30:32,300
he stabbed her in the back.

619
00:30:32,640 --> 00:30:34,840
Let me tell you,
if this is not handled well,

620
00:30:35,444 --> 00:30:36,800
lowering the price is one thing.

621
00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:38,530
They might even cancel the deal.

622
00:30:38,840 --> 00:30:40,680
Mr. He Han, you came in person?

623
00:30:41,160 --> 00:30:42,120
Is the milk tea good?

624
00:30:42,120 --> 00:30:42,920
- Hello, Mr. He Han.
- Hello, Mr. He Han.

625
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:43,560
As long as it tastes good.

626
00:30:43,560 --> 00:30:44,160
Thank you, Mr. He Han.

627
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:45,000
Thanks for the milk tea.

628
00:30:45,080 --> 00:30:46,120
No problem.

629
00:30:46,120 --> 00:30:46,840
Thank you.

630
00:30:47,822 --> 00:30:49,380
We are on the same side, after all.

631
00:30:50,940 --> 00:30:51,730
Look at that.

632
00:30:55,560 --> 00:30:56,280
Do not disturb me.

633
00:30:56,680 --> 00:30:58,080
I came to check on you.

634
00:30:58,240 --> 00:30:58,760
How is it?

635
00:30:59,688 --> 00:31:00,955
How much have you written?

636
00:31:01,600 --> 00:31:02,840
Not even half?

637
00:31:02,840 --> 00:31:04,320
How will you make it, Lin Zhanqiao?

638
00:31:05,644 --> 00:31:06,480
Let me tell you,

639
00:31:06,480 --> 00:31:08,120
you only have one option now.

640
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:09,400
Make it shorter.

641
00:31:09,520 --> 00:31:10,760
The word count does not matter.

642
00:31:10,760 --> 00:31:11,960
Just explain it to readers.

643
00:31:11,960 --> 00:31:13,110
Say the author is not feeling well

644
00:31:13,120 --> 00:31:13,840
and cannot finish.

645
00:31:14,120 --> 00:31:15,320
Or say this chapter is shorter

646
00:31:15,320 --> 00:31:16,520
because the next one will be big.

647
00:31:16,520 --> 00:31:17,600
Explain it however you want.

648
00:31:17,600 --> 00:31:19,530
- Because the next chapter...
- Can you shut up?

649
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:21,560
I am trying to help you.

650
00:31:22,040 --> 00:31:24,200
How long will
Dingqi Platform's editor wait?

651
00:31:24,840 --> 00:31:25,760
At most until 9 PM.

652
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:27,160
With your current state,

653
00:31:27,160 --> 00:31:28,990
you will get 200 words at most by then.

654
00:31:29,020 --> 00:31:30,310
And they still have to review it.

655
00:31:30,320 --> 00:31:31,960
They cannot just publish it.

656
00:31:32,022 --> 00:31:33,200
So you cannot submit at 9 PM.

657
00:31:33,200 --> 00:31:35,440
- You need to submit by 8:50 PM...
- Can you stop talking?

658
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:36,720
Get out!

659
00:31:36,840 --> 00:31:38,240
You just want to see me fail, right?

660
00:31:38,260 --> 00:31:39,500
- I don't.
- You just want to see

661
00:31:39,500 --> 00:31:40,350
Gu Yan miss the update

662
00:31:40,380 --> 00:31:41,933
and watch us make a fool of ourselves!

663
00:31:48,020 --> 00:31:50,720
Dingqi Platform's editor is asking if we
can still submit today.

664
00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:51,740
- They are about to...
- Thank them.

665
00:31:51,760 --> 00:31:52,680
Tell them not to wait.

666
00:31:52,800 --> 00:31:54,488
I will issue a statement tomorrow.

667
00:31:56,080 --> 00:31:57,280
A statement.

668
00:32:22,660 --> 00:32:25,900
(He Han: Chapter 215
Drunk Old Friend, Hidden Depths.docx)

669
00:32:35,260 --> 00:32:37,740
(Chapter 215
Drunk Old Friend, Hidden Depths.docx)

670
00:33:26,280 --> 00:33:26,760
Zhangzhu.

671
00:33:29,240 --> 00:33:29,640
Ms. Lin,

672
00:33:29,800 --> 00:33:31,290
tell Dingqi Platform's editor to wait.

673
00:33:31,520 --> 00:33:32,200
Okay.

674
00:33:34,920 --> 00:33:36,120
This...

675
00:33:40,480 --> 00:33:41,150
Mr. He Han...

676
00:33:43,080 --> 00:33:44,280
I knew he was something else.

677
00:33:45,200 --> 00:33:46,466
You all go back and rest.

678
00:33:46,488 --> 00:33:47,600
You have worked hard all day.

679
00:33:48,222 --> 00:33:50,600
I will input and edit this now
and send it to Dingqi Platform.

680
00:33:50,760 --> 00:33:52,600
You can come to work
two hours later tomorrow.

681
00:33:52,960 --> 00:33:54,200
Okay, I will go tell them.

682
00:33:54,600 --> 00:33:55,080
Remember,

683
00:33:55,600 --> 00:33:56,560
don't mention He Han.

684
00:33:57,560 --> 00:33:58,240
Just say Gu Yan

685
00:33:58,240 --> 00:33:59,360
sent the draft himself.

686
00:34:00,080 --> 00:34:00,580
Understood.

687
00:34:15,511 --> 00:34:16,711
(One new message from one contact.)

688
00:34:16,740 --> 00:34:19,180
(Thank you.)

689
00:34:19,590 --> 00:34:23,060
♪My heart is beating still♪

690
00:34:23,800 --> 00:34:26,830
♪Sometimes I feel alone♪

691
00:34:27,710 --> 00:34:30,630
♪But love should not be frail♪

692
00:34:35,040 --> 00:34:41,980
♪Is there a spell♪

693
00:34:41,980 --> 00:34:45,830
♪That binds and lingers bare♪

694
00:34:48,690 --> 00:34:53,330
♪If there is a way♪

695
00:34:55,080 --> 00:34:55,400
Hello.

696
00:34:57,210 --> 00:34:58,240
It will be done soon.

697
00:34:58,630 --> 00:34:59,320
Really.

698
00:34:59,560 --> 00:35:00,520
At most 45 minutes.

699
00:35:03,610 --> 00:35:06,380
♪I'm nothing but the one♪

700
00:35:06,380 --> 00:35:10,670
♪Who paints the blue sky♪

701
00:35:11,540 --> 00:35:13,080
♪With all of my tears♪

702
00:35:13,080 --> 00:35:14,800
♪And past pain♪

703
00:35:15,060 --> 00:35:16,790
♪I will still try♪

704
00:35:20,140 --> 00:35:23,790
♪Please stay with me♪

705
00:35:24,440 --> 00:35:27,690
♪I could've held you in my arms♪

706
00:35:28,000 --> 00:35:30,750
♪When I said love♪

707
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:31,800
Bye.

708
00:35:31,844 --> 00:35:32,960
- Bye.
- See you tomorrow.

709
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:33,720
- Sleep early.
- Bye.

710
00:35:33,730 --> 00:35:34,490
Bye.

711
00:35:35,200 --> 00:35:36,160
Mr. He Han,

712
00:35:36,520 --> 00:35:38,040
you wrote it so well.

713
00:35:38,120 --> 00:35:39,440
So well!

714
00:35:47,720 --> 00:35:48,920
I really underestimated you.

715
00:35:50,840 --> 00:35:51,640
I am a lawyer.

716
00:35:52,520 --> 00:35:54,240
I always prepare for the worst.

717
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:58,280
About the company,

718
00:35:58,680 --> 00:35:59,790
what did Lawyer Bei tell you?

719
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:02,840
He asked you
to handle some audit issues.

720
00:36:03,533 --> 00:36:05,111
What do you think this company is?

721
00:36:05,600 --> 00:36:06,760
Proof of your relationship?

722
00:36:07,420 --> 00:36:08,840
Or do you think Lawyer Bei loves you,

723
00:36:08,933 --> 00:36:10,866
so he invested in starting
this company for you?

724
00:36:13,333 --> 00:36:14,720
You don't need to use this company

725
00:36:14,720 --> 00:36:16,600
to drive a wedge
between Lawyer Bei and me.

726
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:19,160
I am in my thirties, not eighteen.

727
00:36:19,555 --> 00:36:21,580
I go into business
and start companies with people

728
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:22,800
for one purpose only,

729
00:36:22,911 --> 00:36:23,777
which is making money.

730
00:36:25,100 --> 00:36:26,280
Lawyer Bei has the resources,

731
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:27,577
so why would I not work with him?

732
00:36:28,960 --> 00:36:30,200
Only people your age

733
00:36:30,200 --> 00:36:31,440
think having names together

734
00:36:31,440 --> 00:36:32,560
means a declaration of love.

735
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:34,240
Of course,

736
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:36,440
I am not defending him.

737
00:36:37,160 --> 00:36:38,240
I just want to tell you

738
00:36:38,760 --> 00:36:40,000
I have my own judgment.

739
00:36:40,560 --> 00:36:41,920
Just tell me the facts.

740
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:43,840
If you want facts,

741
00:36:44,160 --> 00:36:44,520
fine.

742
00:36:44,955 --> 00:36:46,333
Let me ask you something.

743
00:36:47,880 --> 00:36:49,240
Do you think a company like yours

744
00:36:49,640 --> 00:36:50,480
is the only one?

745
00:36:52,622 --> 00:36:53,480
Or are there others?

746
00:36:53,520 --> 00:36:54,733
Have you thought about it?

747
00:36:58,266 --> 00:36:59,440
Do you know if there are...

748
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:00,040
I don't know.

749
00:37:00,600 --> 00:37:01,640
You should ask Lawyer Bei.

750
00:37:02,480 --> 00:37:03,560
But from what I can see,

751
00:37:03,800 --> 00:37:05,760
only your company is under audit.

752
00:37:06,160 --> 00:37:07,280
And the risk you face

753
00:37:07,560 --> 00:37:09,400
is heavy back taxes and penalties.

754
00:37:10,960 --> 00:37:11,750
Me or us?

755
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:12,550
You.

756
00:37:13,840 --> 00:37:15,360
From what I can see, Lawyer Bei

757
00:37:15,360 --> 00:37:17,066
has no direct
connection to this company.

758
00:37:20,200 --> 00:37:21,920
So you are saying I was used?

759
00:37:22,440 --> 00:37:23,720
At least, it is not love.

760
00:37:24,840 --> 00:37:26,200
Love should put you first

761
00:37:26,200 --> 00:37:27,200
and be honest with you.

762
00:37:28,955 --> 00:37:30,520
He even knew I was coming to see you.

763
00:37:30,644 --> 00:37:32,666
He should have
explained everything to you.

764
00:37:32,760 --> 00:37:33,680
But did he contact you?

765
00:37:33,920 --> 00:37:34,960
Did he explain anything?

766
00:37:35,680 --> 00:37:37,600
If not, why are you
still entangled with him?

767
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:51,520
Let me ask you.

768
00:37:54,200 --> 00:37:56,280
If the company under
my name has tax issues now,

769
00:37:57,200 --> 00:37:58,440
if you are afraid of trouble,

770
00:37:58,440 --> 00:37:59,620
do you want to stay away from me?

771
00:37:59,630 --> 00:38:01,080
I like taking on trouble.

772
00:38:03,577 --> 00:38:05,933
Otherwise, how would
I earn Lawyer Bei's trust,

773
00:38:07,044 --> 00:38:09,355
and how would I dare pursue you,
Zhou Mei?

774
00:38:22,760 --> 00:38:24,400
You have really surprised me today.

775
00:38:39,910 --> 00:38:45,260
♪If the sky and the sea
turned upside down♪

776
00:38:47,480 --> 00:38:51,110
♪If a swimming fish fell
in love with a flying bird♪

777
00:38:51,820 --> 00:38:53,260
(Mom)

778
00:38:54,560 --> 00:39:01,460
♪If back then we had never let go♪

779
00:39:02,390 --> 00:39:07,490
♪We wouldn't be lost in the crowd♪

780
00:39:09,460 --> 00:39:11,940
♪We met in a thirteenth month♪

781
00:39:11,940 --> 00:39:13,660
♪Held each other in a fifth season♪

782
00:39:13,660 --> 00:39:16,410
♪And found our way back whole♪

783
00:39:17,170 --> 00:39:19,390
♪So let this surging love♪

784
00:39:19,400 --> 00:39:23,890
♪Rise like tides that never fall♪

785
00:39:24,730 --> 00:39:27,710
♪If we're caught in a pouring rain,
that's alright♪

786
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:31,660
♪If we're buried by passing years,
all the better♪

787
00:39:32,170 --> 00:39:34,480
♪At least we still can keep♪

788
00:39:34,480 --> 00:39:38,070
♪This one eternal photograph♪

789
00:40:07,020 --> 00:40:09,980
(Year 2018)

790
00:40:25,680 --> 00:40:26,460
Your turn.

791
00:40:28,920 --> 00:40:30,720
Wake up, your turn.

792
00:40:32,520 --> 00:40:32,960
Really.

793
00:40:33,080 --> 00:40:34,520
Hurry up. Take a look.

794
00:40:34,520 --> 00:40:35,680
Take a look now.

795
00:40:35,680 --> 00:40:36,160
Come.

796
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:36,840
Come.

797
00:40:37,200 --> 00:40:37,840
Good.

798
00:40:37,960 --> 00:40:38,800
You finished writing?

799
00:40:47,880 --> 00:40:48,980
How many fingers?

800
00:40:51,280 --> 00:40:51,640
Three.

801
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:35,560
Hey,

802
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:40,160
are you an eraser or what?

803
00:41:56,500 --> 00:41:59,460
(Year 2018)

804
00:42:06,200 --> 00:42:07,440
First, I would stop you.

805
00:42:08,160 --> 00:42:09,640
But if you insist,

806
00:42:09,755 --> 00:42:11,040
I will go with you and kill them.

807
00:42:11,360 --> 00:42:12,120
No.

808
00:42:12,244 --> 00:42:13,480
Bringing you would slow me down.

809
00:42:13,480 --> 00:42:14,630
I would have to think about your safety.

810
00:42:14,640 --> 00:42:15,720
I would rather go alone.

811
00:42:15,720 --> 00:42:16,250
And...

812
00:42:16,520 --> 00:42:17,680
I don't want to involve you.

813
00:42:18,240 --> 00:42:19,730
But that is not involving me.

814
00:42:20,280 --> 00:42:21,280
And how can you be sure

815
00:42:21,280 --> 00:42:23,360
you alone can kill their whole family

816
00:42:23,360 --> 00:42:24,920
and still get away safely?

817
00:42:25,200 --> 00:42:26,920
I am already prepared to be caught.

818
00:42:26,920 --> 00:42:28,160
I cannot involve you even more.

819
00:42:28,560 --> 00:42:29,560
You have to finish

820
00:42:29,560 --> 00:42:30,640
what I cannot finish for me.

821
00:42:31,120 --> 00:42:32,800
How about this? You charge in,

822
00:42:32,960 --> 00:42:34,111
and I cover you from behind.

823
00:42:34,240 --> 00:42:35,280
You mean we go together?

824
00:42:35,400 --> 00:42:37,400
I go in to kill them,
and you keep watch outside?

825
00:42:37,440 --> 00:42:39,000
Yes. And if it really comes to it,

826
00:42:39,044 --> 00:42:40,280
you can call for help inside,

827
00:42:40,280 --> 00:42:41,222
and I will rush in.

828
00:42:41,577 --> 00:42:43,520
Call for help?
After I kill their whole family,

829
00:42:43,520 --> 00:42:44,460
I call for help?

830
00:42:44,600 --> 00:42:46,288
They should be
the ones calling for help.

831
00:43:05,921 --> 00:43:07,041
(I've been thinking.)

832
00:43:08,321 --> 00:43:11,601
(Everyone's most comfortable level of intimacy)

833
00:43:12,361 --> 00:43:19,691
(is probably different.)

834
00:43:20,691 --> 00:43:22,441
♪If the sky♪

835
00:43:22,951 --> 00:43:24,351
♪And the sea♪

836
00:43:24,891 --> 00:43:26,601
♪Turned upside down♪

837
00:43:28,161 --> 00:43:30,091
♪If a swimming fish♪

838
00:43:30,491 --> 00:43:33,881
♪Fell in love with a flying bird♪

839
00:43:35,651 --> 00:43:37,621
♪If back then♪

840
00:43:37,981 --> 00:43:42,391
♪We had never let go♪

841
00:43:42,991 --> 00:43:49,271
♪We wouldn't be lost in the crowd♪

842
00:43:50,391 --> 00:43:52,541
♪We met in a thirteenth month♪

843
00:43:52,541 --> 00:43:54,411
♪Held each other in a fifth season♪

844
00:43:54,591 --> 00:43:57,031
♪And found our way back whole♪

845
00:43:57,871 --> 00:44:00,041
♪So let this surging love♪

846
00:44:00,041 --> 00:44:04,471
♪Rise like tides that never fall♪

847
00:44:05,371 --> 00:44:07,551
♪If we're caught in a pouring rain♪

848
00:44:07,551 --> 00:44:08,641
♪That's alright♪

849
00:44:09,181 --> 00:44:09,931
♪If we're buried♪

850
00:44:09,931 --> 00:44:12,631
♪By passing years all the better♪

851
00:44:12,891 --> 00:44:15,071
♪At least we still can keep♪

852
00:44:15,251 --> 00:44:19,671
♪This one eternal photograph♪

853
00:44:35,431 --> 00:44:37,721
♪We're on misaligned tracks♪

854
00:44:37,721 --> 00:44:39,481
♪Running in opposite ways♪

855
00:44:39,601 --> 00:44:42,071
♪Searching all along the way♪

856
00:44:42,871 --> 00:44:45,031
♪For the fire of our younger hearts♪

857
00:44:45,221 --> 00:44:50,131
♪And the beauty lost in time♪

858
00:44:50,131 --> 00:44:53,651
♪This time don't lose each other again♪

859
00:44:53,891 --> 00:44:54,861
♪Only after loss♪

860
00:44:54,861 --> 00:44:57,491
♪Do we learn what truly matters most♪

861
00:44:57,901 --> 00:45:00,261
♪In another time and space♪

862
00:45:00,261 --> 00:45:01,821
♪We'll stay and walk together♪

863
00:45:01,821 --> 00:45:04,651
♪Till we grow old♪

864
00:45:05,611 --> 00:45:07,901
♪But still the sky will never♪

865
00:45:07,901 --> 00:45:10,571
♪Turn with the sea♪

866
00:45:13,091 --> 00:45:15,501
♪But still a swimming fish won't♪

867
00:45:15,501 --> 00:45:20,711
♪Fall in love with a flying bird♪
